<Layout::Group {{waypoint "export"}}>

	<Layout::Text text-l text-f>
		<h3><code>GET</code> <code>/export</code> endpoint</h3>
		<p>This HTTP RESTful endpoint exports all data for a specific Namespace and Database.</p>
